					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">A mirror for good measure<br /><br />To clarify: Though $0D is #110011 (dark purple) in the PNG, that's not the case on the actual hardware. Small changes to $0D are something I do to keep certain tools from using $0D when looking for the &quot;first black color in the palette&quot;.</div>

					
